MirrorBooth ToyShaders seed corpus — provenance & licensing
============================================================

Every *.glsl file in this directory is an ORIGINAL work authored for
MirrorBooth and dedicated to the public domain under CC0-1.0 (see LICENSE).
Each file carries an `SPDX-License-Identifier: CC0-1.0` header.

NO code from shadertoy.com (or any third party) is vendored here. These
shaders are fresh implementations of well-known, non-copyrightable graphics
*techniques* (value/fBm noise, voronoi, plasma, kaleidoscope, tunnel,
sphere-trace SDF, domain warp, curl flow, truchet, palette cycling, CRT,
chromatic split, metaballs, starfield, hex mosaic, polar/vignette warps).
They follow the Shadertoy authoring CONVENTION only:

    void mainImage(out vec4 fragColor, in vec2 fragCoord)
    iResolution, iTime, iChannel0

so the deterministic shadertoy_adapter can demonstrate porting them to the
Flutter/Impeller contract and so the RAG index learns realtime idioms.

Adding third-party shaders
--------------------------
Any future non-original file MUST be verified MIT or CC0, carry a per-file
SPDX header, and be listed below with its upstream URL and license. Anything
under Shadertoy's default license (CC-BY-NC-SA) or "all rights reserved"
MUST NOT be added.

